snippet.title: New VR  Platformer coming to Quest and PCVR – VRosty Gameplay and Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Pull-along VRosty, the little snowman, through a warming world in this VR-only puppet-puzzle-platformer. Wishlist now!
